

# --- samples:

---
 Usage: 
       ./ffmpeg_example in-url out-url

Sample: 
       ./ffmpeg_example /dev/video0 /tmp/saved.flv
       vlc /tmp/saved.flv  # display output .flv


---
 Usage: 
       ./ffmpeg_example in-url out-url

Sample: 
       ./ffmpeg_example /dev/video0 /tmp/saved.flv
       vlc /tmp/saved.flv  # display output .flv

---
 Usage: 
       ./ffmpeg_writer_example /path/to/input.jpg /path/to/saved.flv

Sample: 
       ./ffmpeg_writer_example /tmp/1.jpg /tmp/saved.flv
       vlc /tmp/saved.flv  # display output .flv


---
 Usage: 
       ./probe_camera_example

